divs: Sighting DetailsMy family and I was at a restaraunt for dinner . It was a foggy night, as an amateur photographer using my iPhone, I took some pics of the street lights in the parking lot. Upon reviewing the pics I noticed the object in two pics I took one after the other, perhaps a second apart. I zoomed in and saw what looked like a structured craft with 2 lights on the bottom and perhaps a dome one top. In one Of the shots there is the smallest hints of portholes.( though I cant be sure). Because I took them within a second of each other, you Can see it was moving, and moving up.
Summary: Outside in parking lot of restaraunt... Foggy night took Some pics of fog discovered the object later while reviewing photosw
